{"tid":1741041,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國與韓國就軍費談崩，特朗普正在逐步失去盟友","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:32:40.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2079d6117955aa8745ceafc2b7eb0a61e3446896","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/145E0/production/_109742438_f1fd4089-6f5b-4553-ad7d-6fce4d3546ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F145E0%2Fproduction%2F_109742438_f1fd4089-6f5b-4553-ad7d-6fce4d3546ea.jpg&h=c1d03ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">韓國國防部長鄭景斗和美國國防部長埃斯珀11月15日舉行會晤。此次美國與韓國討論《日韓軍事情報保護協定》續簽，調整聯合軍演行動，增攤軍費等議題。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國與韓國近70年的軍事同盟關係，罕見出現了公開裂痕，而這一情況出現的同時，美國試圖說服韓國與日本續簽《日韓軍事情報保護協定》的努力也沒有達到預期的效果。<br />\n<br />\n周二（11月19日），美國與韓國在首爾舉行的最新一輪《韓美防衛費分擔特別協定》談判不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n韓國首席談判代表鄭恩甫透露，美國的總體提議和韓國的原則立場之間有著相當大的差距。用數字簡單來說，也就是美國方面要求韓國為美國駐軍出資50億美元，而韓國只願意承擔約10億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">韓國媒體稱美國的要求是「獅子大開口」，韓國民眾和團體最近已經就此舉行多次抗議示威，因為美國要求的50億美元，相當於現在韓國分擔費用的5倍之多。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據現行《駐韓美軍地位協定》規定，韓國分擔金用於支付駐韓美軍韓籍僱員的工資、美軍基地建設費用、軍需後勤這三個項目。<br />\n<br />\n但是美國要求韓國同時承擔駐韓美軍補貼、出動戰略武器費用等新項目，對此韓國表示不能同意。<br />\n<br />\n在駐韓美軍費用問題上，美國總統特朗普一直堅持韓國應該支付更多。特朗普甚至暗示從韓國全部撤軍，而如今美國擺在談判桌上的50億美元，<span style=\"color: red;\">似乎尋的也是特朗普的思路。他曾經提及美國為韓國境內和周邊駐軍所提供的保護「價值50億美元」。</span><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，特朗普要求日本為駐日美軍提供的經費增加至目前的4倍左右，約80億美元，因特朗普認為日美安保條約&ldquo;不公平&rdquo;。<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">表演型策略</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n自特朗普上任以來，一系列舉措讓盟友寒心。<span style=\"color: red;\">中美貿易戰，對歐盟加征關稅，與墨西哥和加拿大重新簽署北美貿易協議，向日本、韓國不僅索要更多軍費還重新談判了貿易協議。</span><br />\n <br />\n最近，德國總理默克爾直接拒絕了美國的提議，並且在北約會議上和特朗普發生爭吵，決定將不再向北約繳納軍費。<br />\n <br />\n特朗普要求德國將軍費提高至530億美元，占GDP的2.7%，這對已經脆弱的德國經濟是一個稱重的壓力。<br />\n <br />\n如果特朗普連任，接下來4年美國的盟友會對美國持懷疑態度，並不會全力支持美國的全球戰略。<br />\n <br />\n自上任以來，特朗普將他的上任演藝帶到了國際政壇上，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然部分降低了其他國家&ldquo;占美國的便宜&rdquo;，但外交方面可以說是失敗的，因為美國的傳統盟友正在對美國表達前所未有的不滿。</span><br />\n <br />\n在各種談判中，特朗普一會憤怒、一會熱情，並擔任了一個永不滿足的談判者的角色。如果對方不接受他的條件，就會將更嚴厲的舉措和威脅捆綁在一起。<br />\n <br />\n然而，特朗普的策略似乎讓談判變得更複雜，加劇了全球經濟和政治的不確定性。<span style=\"color: red;\">我們可以看到，中國與歐盟並沒有向特朗普妥協。</span><br />\n <br />\n目前，美國農民的情況並不樂觀，部分企業公開表示對特朗普政策的不滿，因為不確定性讓他們遭到嚴重損失。<br />\n <br />\n特朗普專注於表演而不是實質內容，這讓他的支持者都掩飾不住因此帶來的挫敗感，同時讓他們深覺煩惱的是：特朗普並不想結束他的表演。"},{"pid":"e953ed2569f2ed152cc5a8f7b92af75e58122d3f","tid":1741041,"uid":57424,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"香港可以比<br />\n派軍黎香港"},{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},{"pid":"a79f6085f0500d90b651f6c7195ab8518ca844af","tid":1741041,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"減少駐軍 但可以增加售武"},{"pid":"e9d735303a951e6a411a2c95166e6ba3000a0011","tid":1741041,"uid":226466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"50 億美元<br />\n<br />\n香港呢派出糧俾克警都出咗1x億美元<br />\n<br />\n好似美軍抵d<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aae614da105727462b3db05de89f72ef0eb9915","tid":1741041,"uid":262674,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"安心先啦起碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6617f18e7248aa559cc53d7b2c976ad2f71eb8e2","tid":1741041,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"狗隊經費一年有冇50億美元？"},{"pid":"42a9f7401d2a276f0d12b3aa69c036a0d1f69782","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗搞大白象 利益輸送 果度都多上千億儲備頂<br />\n<br />\n20年夠香港重新起飛"},{"pid":"e448afdee0905fcda083f98547bec1ade62b1341","tid":1741041,"uid":315851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e953ed2569f2ed152cc5a8f7b92af75e58122d3f","tid":1741041,"uid":57424,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"香港可以比<br />\n派軍黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"yes,香港想課都冇得課<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b17888f0d5a368466840880bbb5ff8dac9fe223","tid":1741041,"uid":196750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"樓上班五毛低能仔：認清楚系邊個求邊個先？美國正失去南韓？屌你老母臭西啦，唔通你班五毛要南韓投向小學豬頭雜種？？"},{"pid":"53e0ee2694ca6b42a83924ebae9b5be60cad0009","tid":1741041,"uid":196750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2079d6117955aa8745ceafc2b7eb0a61e3446896","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/145E0/production/_109742438_f1fd4089-6f5b-4553-ad7d-6fce4d3546ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F145E0%2Fproduction%2F_109742438_f1fd4089-6f5b-4553-ad7d-6fce4d3546ea.jpg&h=c1d03ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">韓國國防部長鄭景斗和美國國防部長埃斯珀11月15日舉行會晤。此次美國與韓國討論《日韓軍事情報保護協定》續簽，調整聯合軍演行動，增攤軍費等議題。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國與韓國近70年的軍事同盟關係，罕見出現了公開裂痕，而這一情況出現的同時，美國試圖說服韓國與日本續簽《日韓軍事情報保護協定》的努力也沒有達到預期的效果。<br />\n<br />\n周二（11月19日），美國與韓國在首爾舉行的最新一輪《韓美防衛費分擔特別協定》談判不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n韓國首席談判代表鄭恩甫透露，美國的總體提議和韓國的原則立場之間有著相當大的差距。用數字簡單來說，也就是美國方面要求韓國為美國駐軍出資50億美元，而韓國只願意承擔約10億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">韓國媒體稱美國的要求是「獅子大開口」，韓國民眾和團體最近已經就此舉行多次抗議示威，因為美國要求的50億美元，相當於現在韓國分擔費用的5倍之多。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據現行《駐韓美軍地位協定》規定，韓國分擔金用於支付駐韓美軍韓籍僱員的工資、美軍基地建設費用、軍需後勤這三個項目。<br />\n<br />\n但是美國要求韓國同時承擔駐韓美軍補貼、出動戰略武器費用等新項目，對此韓國表示不能同意。<br />\n<br />\n在駐韓美軍費用問題上，美國總統特朗普一直堅持韓國應該支付更多。特朗普甚至暗示從韓國全部撤軍，而如今美國擺在談判桌上的50億美元，<span style=\"color: red;\">似乎尋的也是特朗普的思路。他曾經提及美國為韓國境內和周邊駐軍所提供的保護「價值50億美元」。</span><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，特朗普要求日本為駐日美軍提供的經費增加至目前的4倍左右，約80億美元，因特朗普認為日美安保條約&ldquo;不公平&rdquo;。<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">表演型策略</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n自特朗普上任以來，一系列舉措讓盟友寒心。<span style=\"color: red;\">中美貿易戰，對歐盟加征關稅，與墨西哥和加拿大重新簽署北美貿易協議，向日本、韓國不僅索要更多軍費還重新談判了貿易協議。</span><br />\n <br />\n最近，德國總理默克爾直接拒絕了美國的提議，並且在北約會議上和特朗普發生爭吵，決定將不再向北約繳納軍費。<br />\n <br />\n特朗普要求德國將軍費提高至530億美元，占GDP的2.7%，這對已經脆弱的德國經濟是一個稱重的壓力。<br />\n <br />\n如果特朗普連任，接下來4年美國的盟友會對美國持懷疑態度，並不會全力支持美國的全球戰略。<br />\n <br />\n自上任以來，特朗普將他的上任演藝帶到了國際政壇上，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然部分降低了其他國家&ldquo;占美國的便宜&rdquo;，但外交方面可以說是失敗的，因為美國的傳統盟友正在對美國表達前所未有的不滿。</span><br />\n <br />\n在各種談判中，特朗普一會憤怒、一會熱情，並擔任了一個永不滿足的談判者的角色。如果對方不接受他的條件，就會將更嚴厲的舉措和威脅捆綁在一起。<br />\n <br />\n然而，特朗普的策略似乎讓談判變得更複雜，加劇了全球經濟和政治的不確定性。<span style=\"color: red;\">我們可以看到，中國與歐盟並沒有向特朗普妥協。</span><br />\n <br />\n目前，美國農民的情況並不樂觀，部分企業公開表示對特朗普政策的不滿，因為不確定性讓他們遭到嚴重損失。<br />\n <br />\n特朗普專注於表演而不是實質內容，這讓他的支持者都掩飾不住因此帶來的挫敗感，同時讓他們深覺煩惱的是：特朗普並不想結束他的表演。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"白癡仔，美國農民反侵侵？有冇數據？邊個反佢？美農一直係侵侵票倉，你老母臭西雜種派你班五毛去美國做農民就形成反侵勢力啦！你老母垃圾報導講嘢靠吹！"},{"pid":"d0ea7fda298aebf58eeeb2f6e2e944480ebbdb71","tid":1741041,"uid":287577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"比錢人(USA)保護自己<br />\n&amp;<br />\n比錢人(Chinazi)侵犯自己<br />\n兩種唔同既概念。"},{"pid":"269654edfac0e2451b58938c39d3e57e3aee83f0","tid":1741041,"uid":45727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6617f18e7248aa559cc53d7b2c976ad2f71eb8e2","tid":1741041,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f88cf89f8e057b8445a2dbc19212529c5aae064c","tid":1741041,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cd10745ae286e9989620d3036127269e77713e5f","tid":1741041,"uid":237517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港比10倍 駐軍香港ok?"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/images/Expenditure_TC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fimages%2FExpenditure_TC.png&h=38d71766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50億美金,對香港黎講都唔係輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"狗隊經費一年有冇50億美元？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"一年200億港紙"},{"pid":"e3144a